lead_paragraph: Lakota Beatty scored 20 points, Maria Martianez had 18 points with 13 rebounds and Oral Roberts used an 18-0 run in the fourth quarter to shock No. 12 Oklahoma 74-67 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Oral Roberts Women Stun No. 12 Oklahoma With Late 18-0 Run
